cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving Single-Image Super-Resolution using Convolutional Neural Networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses methods for expanding the receptive field of the network, which is related to the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed approach in terms of accuracy, parameter count, and speed, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
